### Welcome
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products

###

### Get Single Product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1

###

### Get Product - Not Found (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/999

###

### Get Products by Category
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/category/electronics

###

### Category - Not Found (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/category/furniture

###

### Add New Product (201 Created)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bluetooth Speaker",
  "category": "electronics",
  "price": 1499,
  "stock": 30,
  "description": "Portable speaker with 12-hour battery life"
}

###

### Add Duplicate Product (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bluetooth Speaker",
  "category": "electronics",
  "price": 1499,
  "stock": 30
}

###

### Validation Error - Bad Data (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": -100
}

###

### Add Item to Cart
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Add Another Item to Cart
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "productId": 4,
  "quantity": 3
}

###

### Add Item - Not Enough Stock (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "productId": 3,
  "quantity": 100
}

###

### View Cart
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/user123

###

### View Empty Cart
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/newuser

###

### Checkout (201 Created)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123"
}

###

### Checkout Empty Cart - Error (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123"
}

###

### Unknown Route - 404
GET http://localhost:3000/api/unknown
